window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>He’s a savage.</b></p> <p>Damien Cross treats New York City as if it’s his personal playground.</p> <p>He sees.</p> <p>He touches.</p> <p>He conquers.</p> <p>He holds the fate of my family in his hands.</p> <p>And makes a deal with me I can’t refuse.</p> <p>He’ll forgive my father’s debt if he can have something in exchange: me.</p> <p>I promised myself I wouldn’t get addicted, but nothing is guaranteed when you make a deal with a savage.</p> <p>Now this debt is my cross to bear.</p>"; 
